#
# edit - Find a file in your $PATH to edit, or if an absolute path
#        is provided, edit that file instead. If a non-existent
#        file is supplied, use that. If nothing is provided,
#        edit a temp file in $TMPDIR.
#        Use $EDITOR if defined, otherwise default back to vi.
